Ok. maybe i didnt get the message across in my last message. That, or gladiator@yahoogroups.com deleted the subliminal message i embedded within the thread. 
PLEASE visit my webpage. PLEASE read gladiator_story.rtf. failure to do so will result in a gang of blood-thirsty orcs coming into your house, howling at your dog, and eating the corpses you have stashed in your basement.
A big part of writing this is to get positive feedback from other people reading it. If i don't get feedback, i kind of lack the incentive needed to continue writing. I was hoping for some big appreciation from 'Triad' and Dancing Corpse after finishing chapter 6/7. Also, getting some feedback from the big man upstairs (Tom Ricket of course) would be cool also.

-Zjack
